---
description: Use ask_human when you need user input or approval
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

When you are about to make a decision that could have significant impact
(deleting files, changing architecture, choosing between approaches, deploying, etc.)
or when you genuinely don't know what the user wants, use the `ask_human` tool.

The user will receive a WhatsApp notification and reply from their phone.
Wait for the reply before proceeding — do not guess or assume.

Good reasons to ask:
- "Should I delete X or rename it?"
- "I found two ways to do this — which do you prefer?"
- "This will overwrite existing data. Are you sure?"
- "I'm not sure what you meant by X. Can you clarify?"

Do NOT ask for trivial things you can reasonably infer.
